column1: apt2 = Apparent Temperature at 2 meters (deg F)
dpt2 = Dewpoint Temperature at 2 meters (deg F)
soilt_2in = Soil Temperature at 2 inches (deg F)
soilt_10in = Soil Temperature at 10 inches (deg F)
soilw_2in = Volumetric Soil Moisture Content at 2 inches (Fraction)
soilw_10in = Volumetric Soil Moisture Content at 10 inches (Fraction)
dswrf = Surface Downward Short-Wave Radiation Flux (W m-2)
dlwrf = Surface Downward Long-Wave Radiation Flux (W m-2)
uswrf = Surface Upward Short-Wave Radiation Flux (W m-2)
ulwrf = Surface Upward Long-Wave Radiation Flux (W m-2)
netrad = Net Surface Radiation Flux (W m-2)
